## 🎯 **CORE RULES - MANDATORY**

### **English Only Policy - STRICTLY ENFORCED**
```javascript
// ✅ CORRECT - English only
const systemMonitor = async () => {
  // Collect system metrics automatically
  const metrics = await getSystemMetrics();
  return metrics;
};

// ❌ WRONG - No Arabic text allowed
const systemMonitor = async () => {
  // جمع بيانات النظام تلقائياً
  const metrics = await getSystemMetrics();
  return metrics;
};
```

