- **Service Detection:** Auto-detect running services (Ollama, APIs)

### **Ollama Integration Standards**
- **Local Models:** Support for llama3, llama3.2, mistral, codellama
- **Auto-Detection:** Automatic model discovery and configuration
- **API Endpoints:** Both OpenAI-compatible and native Ollama APIs
- **Performance:** Sub-second response times required
- **Privacy:** All processing stays on local machine

